title: Sublime Text 3 (3083) Mac
description:
Sublime Text 3 (3083) Mac
=========================

This torrent only consists of the patched sublime text
 3 portable build 3083 zip archives and installers for
 x32 and x64 (the installers are not patched).

It contains the following files:

* Sublime Text Build 3083.dmg
* Sublime Text patched
* Sublime Text unpatched
* info.txt
* Sublime-Text-3-3083-Mac--md5-list.chks

This is how you install sublime text 3:

- Run 'Sublime Text Build 3083.dmg'
- Copy 'Sublime Text patched' as 'Sublime Text' to the installation directory

You can check the files using md5sum like this:

$ md5sum -c ./Sublime-Text-3-3083-Mac--md5-list.chks

Or just compare the md5 checksums you generate from the
 downloaded files to these (same order as above):

* f0c62921e5785bf21df26b45c6087c74
* 5b00fe8fcd31ace5129909d70677ff7a
* 1181b0742c50063d27d910b8e98a8d22
* 14f20ca8b65541360063bc9151b83bb6
   This last one (of 'info.txt') can be different

Thanks for downloading 'Sublime Text 3 3083 Mac' and
 keep seeding! :)
